    <h1>Subject Line</h1>
    <p class="description">The first line of text recipients see in their inbox before opening an email. Subject lines are the <strong>single biggest lever on email open rates</strong> — and one of the first signals email providers use to decide whether a message reaches the inbox at all.</p>
